<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <meta name="description" content="User Registration Email Template." />
  <title>INAE Membership Application Response</title>
  <style type="text/css">
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f2f3f8;
      font-family: "Open Sans", sans-serif;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
      width: 100% !important;
      height: 100% !important;
    }

    table {
      border-spacing: 0;
      border-collapse: collapse;
    }

    img {
      display: block;
      max-width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline !important;
    }

    .email-wrapper {
      max-width: 570px;
      width: 100%;
      margin: 20px auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 18px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
      padding: 20px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      background-color: #e9ecef;
    }

    .logo {
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .divider {
      border-top: 1px solid #cecece;
      margin: 25px 0;
      width: 100%;
    }

    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 30px;
    }

    .footer p {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: rgba(69, 80, 86, 0.74);
      line-height: 18px;
    }

    @media screen and (max-width: 600px) {
      .email-wrapper {
        padding: 15px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div>
    <table align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" class="email-wrapper">
      <tr>
        <td style="text-align: center; padding: 20px; background-color: #edf2fb">
          <a href="https://www.inae.in/" title="logo" target="_blank">
            <img width="400" src="https://www.inae.in/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/logon.png" alt="" title="logo" />
          </a>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="background-color: #f5f3f4">
        <td>
          <div style="padding: 18px">
            <h4 style="
                  font-size: 18px;
                  color: #1e1e2d;
                  font-weight: 700;
                  text-align: left;
                ">
              Dear <%= applicant_Name %>,
            </h4>
            <p style="
                  font-size: 16px;
                  color: #1e1e2d;
                  text-align: left;
                  text-align: justify;
                ">
              Wishing you the best in your future endeavours. If you have any questions or need any
              more help, feel free to reach us.

            </p>
            <p style="
                  font-size: 16px;
                  color: #1e1e2d;
                  text-align: left;
                  text-align: justify;
                ">
              We appreciate your interest in Individual Membership of INAE and your effort in submitting
              your application.

            </p>
            <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #1e1e2d; text-align: justify">
              Following a thorough review of your application against the eligibility criteria by the
              committee, we regret to inform you that we are unable to process your application further
              at this time. We encourage you to stay informed about future opportunities with INAE.

            </p>
            <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #1e1e2d; text-align: justify">
              INAE wishes you the best in your future endeavours.

            </p>
            <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #1e1e2d; text-align: justify">
              Should you have any questions or require any further assistance, please do not hesitate
              to contact Membership Team at INAE.
            </p>
            <div class="divider"></div>
            <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #1e1e2d; text-align: left">
              With regards,<br />
              Secretariat<br />
              <span style="font-weight: bold">Indian National Academy of Engineering (INAE)<br /></span><br />
              Ground Floor, Block-II,<br />
              Technology Bhavan,<br />
              Mehrauli Road,<br />
              New Delhi-110 016.<br />
              Phone: 011-26582475<br />
              Website:
              <a href="https://www.inae.in/" style="color: #402e7a; text-decoration: none">www.inae.in</a>
            </p>
          </div>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td class="footer">
          <p>
            &copy;
            <a href="https://www.inae.in/" style="color: rgba(69, 80, 86, 0.74); text-decoration: none"><strong>www.inae.in</strong></a>
          </p>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </div>
</body>

</html>